The finals of the champions league has ended with Real Madrid defeating Liverpool 1-0 in France to claim their 14th Champions league Cup. During the match yesterday, Some Real Madrid players were caught on Camera jubilating after their hardworking Goalkeeper, Courtois Blocked Several attempts from the Legendary Footballer, Mohamed Salah.
The pictures of the Moments that the Goalkeeper, Courtois Blocked the attempts of Salah were shared on social media where a lot of football fans reacted to the pictures.
Take a look at the pictures of how the Real Madrid players reacted when their Goalkeeper, Courtois Blocked Several Attempts from Mohamed Salah Below.
Real Madrid fans reacted to the pictures on Instagram. Check out how they Reacted in the screenshots below.
Real Madrid Goalkeeper, Courtois was certainly the man of the match as he saved several shots on goal by Liverpool. Liverpool had 23 attempts on goal and six shots on target with all counting for nothing.


